name: W_SERIES_004: The Puffin
description: A towering monster stands knee deep in a sea of grey water. It is a monster made of battered and rusting metal; a massive mechanical biped. Dozens of tiny human figures paddle around it in small wooden boats, giving the thing a wide berth but otherwise seemingly oblivious to its immense presence. The humans seem to be fishermen, casting nets, calling instructions to each other and busily going about their arduous work as the MECH that looms over them wades further and further out into the deepening waters.
